        {
            "title": "Axios稱美國國防部接近與Anthropic切斷關係 雙方就AI軍事用途存分歧",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據Axios報導，美國國防部接近切斷與<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a>的關係，並可能將這家人工智能(AI)公司列為一項供應鏈風險，此前對公司技術使用方面的限制感到不滿。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Axios引述一位熟悉相關討論但未具名的消息人士稱，雙方此前圍繞美國軍方可如何使用Claude工具進行了長達數月的激烈磋商，關係幾近破裂。報導稱，Anthropic尤其希望確保其AI不會被用於大規模監控公民，或用於開發無需人類參與即可部署的武器。報導稱，美國政府方面則希望能夠將Claude用於「所有合法用途」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3b581254-6632-312b-a4ac-0d7e44e82727-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Axios引述一名五角大樓高級別官員稱，若Anthropic被認定為供應鏈風險，任何希望與國防部開展業務的公司都將被迫與Anthropic撇清關係。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「戰爭部與Anthropic的關係正在評估中，」五角大樓發言人Sean Parnell在電郵聲明中稱。「我們國家要求我們的夥伴願意幫助作戰人員贏下每一場戰鬥。最終，它關乎我們的部隊，以及美國人民的安全。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic的一位發言人則對Axios表示，公司與五角大樓正在「以真誠的態度進行富有成效的對話」，並表示公司致力於將AI用於國家安全。Anthropic的一位代表未立即回應彭博的置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年，Anthropic贏得了美國國防部一項為期兩年的協議，內容涉及Claude Gov模型原型以及Claude企業版（Claude for Enterprise）。Axios稱，Anthropic與軍方的談判可能為未來與OpenAI、谷歌和xAI的磋商定下基調；這些公司的模型尚未用於涉密工作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic由前OpenAI研究人員創立，將自身定位為更負責任的AI公司，旨在避免這項先進技術引發災難性危害。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Pentagon Is Close to Cutting Ties With Anthropic, Axios Says (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/axios%E7%A8%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E8%88%87anthropic%E5%88%87%E6%96%B7%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-%E9%9B%99%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%B1ai%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E5%AD%98%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A7-151341182.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-17 00:46:11",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利調整歐洲投資銀行業務領導層",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 摩根士丹利對歐洲投資銀行業務領導層進行了一系列調整，此舉正值該地區併購活動料將出現激增之際。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博新聞社看到的內部備忘錄顯示，這家美國銀行任命William Bertagna擔任歐洲、中東和非洲地區投資銀行業務副主管。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bertagna將接替Martin Grebner的職位，後者與Markus Fimpel共同獲選執掌該行歐洲、中東和非洲地區工業組。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前領導該地區工業組的Karsten Hofacker將轉任歐洲、中東和非洲地區金融保薦人併購業務主管。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-369f6f26-592d-3bec-b77b-24c1be23667b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利發言人證實了備忘錄內容。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Morgan Stanley Shuffles Investment Banking Leaders in Europe (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E9%A0%98%E5%B0%8E%E5%B1%A4-124940262.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 22:08:08",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "法國對提升歐元國際地位的努力有所顧慮 呼籲評估相關經濟風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 法國政府對歐洲尋求加強歐元國際地位的努力有所顧慮，呼籲評估相關經濟風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:歐元區;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐元區\">歐元區</a>財長將於周一晚些時候在布魯塞爾會面，討論如何在發行與交易中促進歐元的使用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一名法國財政部官員匿名向記者吹風時表示，巴黎支持這項努力，但希望更深入地了解：如果該舉措進一步推高歐元兌美元匯率，出口商將為此付出怎樣的代價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國歷來是提升歐元在全球經濟中分量的積極支持者，也經常抱怨美元的主導地位。相關情緒最早可追溯至20世紀60年代，當時法國前總統Valery Giscard D’Estaing提出「過度特權」一詞，用以形容美元享有的特殊地位。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7d951872-f2e7-3d3a-8738-45487d886464-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，這名法國官員表示，歐元區經濟如今未必能夠復制這種特權，部分原因在於歐元區對世界其他地區存在貿易順差。該人士稱，如果在危機時刻歐元成為投資者的避險資產，歐元區出口商將同時遭受兩重打擊：經濟下行時需求的下降，以及歐元的升值。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題France Sees Reasons for Caution on Bolstering Euro’s Global Role</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%89%80%E9%A1%A7%E6%85%AE-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%A9%95%E4%BC%B0%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-143141552.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 23:34:39",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "伊朗外長與國際原子能機構總幹事舉行會談 美伊新一輪談判即將展開",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 伊朗外長阿巴斯·阿拉格齊周一在日內瓦與聯合國原子能機構負責人舉行會談，為即將與美國展開的第二輪核談判做準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:伊朗國家電視台;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/伊朗國家電視台\">伊朗國家電視台</a>報導稱，阿拉格齊在與國際原子能機構總幹事拉斐爾·馬裡亞諾·格羅西會談時，討論了將於周二與美國特使史蒂夫·威特科夫進行的間接會談中將提出的「方案」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務卿馬爾科·盧比奧向記者表示，他對德黑蘭與華盛頓能克服多年緊張對峙與敵意、最終達成協議「抱有希望」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「與伊朗達成實質性協議向來困難重重，因為我們面對的是依據神學而非地緣政治決策的激進神職人員。但且看事態發展，我希望談判能成功，我們都希望如此。」盧比奧說。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-02cab32a-7068-3f1e-a7a7-3a1f27c02359-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普曾威脅稱，除非伊朗同意達成限制其核計畫的協議以換取制裁解除，否則將對伊朗發動打擊。針對伊朗政權近期鎮壓大規模抗議活動並造成人員死亡，川普已在伊朗附近調集了軍艦和戰鬥機。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：油價波動 伊朗在美伊新一輪會談前舉行演練</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據伊朗半官方塔斯尼姆通訊社報導，伊朗伊斯蘭革命衛隊周一在霍爾木茲海峽附近舉行演練。這凸顯出石油資源豐富的波斯灣地區緊張局勢持續升溫。報導稱，演練涉及對該戰略性航道的「智能控制」，演練重點關注對潛在安全威脅作出「快速、果斷且全面的反應」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普的女婿賈裡德·庫什納預計將於周二與威特科夫共同率領美國代表團參與會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Iran Meets UN Nuclear Chief Before Next Round of US Talks (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jonathan Tirone、Eric Martin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E8%88%87%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E8%83%BD%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%B8%BD%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%B0-%E8%BC%AA%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B-141942452.html",
